{"tid":2511378,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"FB 仇恨言論懲罰數升 400%    「不會因政治取態移除貼文」","createTime":"2021-05-01T00:51:32.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-01T01:04:55.000Z","uid":105567,"like":0,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"59e9a6dae1d9dfd004d21c148d4a762553eb5ee9","tid":2511378,"uid":105567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T00:51:32.000Z","msg":"近日 Facebook 的內容政策經理 Manu Gummi 在傳媒簡介會上介紹 Facebook 對仇恨言論的新政策安排，並透露 Facebook 對仇恨言論的主動發現率高達 97.1%，在 2019 至 2020 年期間對仇恨言論的懲罰數量也升了接近 400%。<br />\n<br />\nManu Gummi 強調為了讓用戶能在網絡上更舒適和自在地發言，Facebook 有責任保障用戶不會因為自己的身份而遭受攻擊。因此 Facebook 的內容政策團隊每兩星期便會召開會議討論和調整政策，確保每名用戶能在和諧自由的環境下瀏覽 Facebook。<br />\n<br />\n對於短短一兩年間發現並處理仇恨言論的比率極速增加，Facebook 指是由於 AI 的進步令其更有效判斷出相關內容有否涉及仇恨和歧視字眼。而對於被外界質疑 Facebook 的言論審查制度有否存在政治考量，Manu Gummi 則強調 Facebook 不會有政治立場，更不會因政治取態而移除用戶的貼文。<br />\n<br />\n早前 Facebook 旗下 Instagram 也推出了「隱藏文字」的新功能，讓用戶可以過濾一些可能帶有冒犯性的詞語、句子和 Emoji 表情符號。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2021/04/30/fbhatespeech/fun-tech/?fbclid=IwAR2nsHXCV6l6R3Ugi0vHSD9mAjdl9Jm69GcGDbFdCzmdoYPdYnlnEf-dmRk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2021%2F04%2F30%2Ffbhatespeech%2Ffun-tech%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR2nsHXCV6l6R3Ugi0vHSD9mAjdl9Jm69GcGDbFdCzmdoYPdYnlnEf-dmRk&d=TdbSzDXFtRyzmt3f81zqRLO6ciNacqKxYXGqE8pVUEM%3D&h=a33ee3e1\" target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2021/04/30/fbhatespeech/fun-tech/?fbclid=IwAR2nsHXCV6l6R3Ugi0vHSD9mAjdl9Jm69GcGDbFdCzmdoYPdYnlnEf-dmRk</a>"},{"pid":"e6e021ca25a1aae765489773879c9cc4811920c7","tid":2511378,"uid":33874,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T00:55:20.000Z","msg":"我都信佢唔會<br />\n直接ban ac姐"},{"pid":"44a6e3595b8b9127a94063452de8ee6aa1e6ea49","tid":2511378,"uid":297997,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T00:55:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmbwDpERZwBuK2Xgc6tW3MAcBqw4WWKMufqv7rRMD7CgC2?filename=BrVjoUF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx